---
// Hero section — leads with positioning statement (not name)
// Per design-refinement: positioning statement is the visual headline
---

<section class="text-center space-y-6" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <!-- Positioning statement — the visual headline -->
  <h1
    id="hero-heading"
    class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary leading-tight"
  >
    Exploring ways to apply engineering principles to the AI coding landscape.
  </h1>

  <!-- Name and title — clearly secondary in visual weight -->
  <div>
    <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-base-content">Greg Brewer</p>
    <p class="text-base text-base-content/60 font-medium mt-1">
      Founder &middot; CTO &middot; AI Engineer
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tagline — present but understated -->
  <p class="text-base text-base-content/60 leading-relaxed italic">
    I build systems that help people make better decisions.
  </p>
</section>
